iana.encoding_considerations:
The material is binary and must be suitably encoded on
   non-binary transports.

Security considerations: This file format is protected against 
   tampering, and a file's origin can be verified using digital 
   signatures.  Posession of a file constitutes permission to call a 
   specific number on the account of a specific gateway customer; 
   distribution of the file should be protected accordingly.

Interoperability considerations: None

Published specification: None

Applications which use this media type: Phone Doubler Quick Call,
   Phone Doubler
